item.title: CVE-2023-6926|2024-01-23T19:23:08.788Z -- crestron -- am-300
item.description: There is an OS command injection vulnerability in Crestron AM-300 firmware version 1.4499.00018 which may enable a user of a limited-access SSH session to escalate their privileges to root-level access.
